-- UNITED STATES; RELIGIOUS ORGANIZATIONS; EXTRACURRICULAR ACTIVITIES; 
SEPARATION OF CHURCH AND STATE; FIRST AMENDMENT; FREEDOM OF RELIGION; PRAYER 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
