<TEXT>
<P>
A mobile home at Coastal Trailer Villa near Bay Park was ruled a total loss 
after a Monday morning blaze. 
</P>
<P>
No one was home, and no injuries were reported. 
</P>
<P>
The mobile home in the 1500 block of Morena Blvd was destroyed in the 8:40 a.m. 
fire with $14,000 in damage. 
</P>
<P>
The fire, believed caused by discarded smoking material, began in a cabana area 
and spread to the mobile home. 
</P>
