<P>
Stay Up Some More With Jay and Dave: Night-owl TV fans who tune in talk-show 
host David Letterman and fill-in funnyman Jay Leno have years to enjoy more 
wise-cracking monologues, witty interviews and stupid pet tricks. NBC said 
Monday it has signed Letterman and Leno, the sole guest host on "The Tonight 
Show Starring Johnny Carson," to new multiyear contracts. No further details 
were disclosed. GREG BRAXTON 
