</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Depeche Blue: Depeche Mode has added a second Dodger Stadium concert for Aug. 
5. Their Aug. 4 show sold out one hour after tickets went on sale last 
Saturday. Tickets for the added show go on sale this Saturday at 9 a.m. at 
Music Plus stores and through Ticketmaster. GREG BRAXTON 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA060590-0108 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 229224 </DOCID>
